OL,3,CIsland that inspired Agatha Christie
OL,4,Cnovels no longer up for sale
OL,6,FAn historic hotel in south Devon with
OL,7,Flinks to the writer Agatha Christie
OL,8,Fhas been taken off the market after
OL,9,Fits owner secured an extra #5 million
OL,10,Fto refurbish it.
OL,12,FBurgh Island, off the coast of Bigbury-
OL,13,Fon-Sea, is renowned as the inspiration
OL,14,Ffor two murder mysteries, after the
OL,15,Fwriter stayed in the Grade II-listed
OL,16,Fhotel there.
OL,18,FIn its time, the art deco building has
OL,19,Falso hosted Winston Churchill and The
OL,20,FBeatles.
