OL,3,CIsland that inspired Agatha Christie
OL,4,Cnovels no longer up for sale
OL,6,FThe island and hotel were sold in 2018
OL,7,Ffor approximately #8.4million and four
OL,8,Fyears later it won planning
OL,9,Fpermissions for up to #10 million of
OL,10,Fdevelopment, including another 12
OL,11,Fsuites, a new restaurant, a bar and
OL,12,Fmore staff accommodation.
OL,14,FThe owners, Giles Fuchs and his sister
OL,15,FNicky bought into the hotel six years
OL,16,Fago.
OL,18,FIt was always the deal with the other
OL,19,Finvestors that the property would be
OL,20,Fsold after five years.
