OL,6,FBut after one year on the market, and
OL,7,Fa sale that fell through, the pair
OL,8,Fhave now secured new funding that
OL,9,Fmeans they can keep the hotel and take
OL,10,Fit into the future.
OL,12,FNew windows and a new roof have
OL,13,Falready been put in and renewable
OL,14,Fenergy heating including ground source
OL,15,Fand solar will take this historic
OL,16,Fhotel into the future.
